description:
Applicability
This schedule applies to: 1) commercial and industrial customers for general power use with a demand of 7,000 kW and over, and 2) services where other Rate Schedules (other than Rate Schedules NM and SG) do not apply. This schedule is applicable on an annual basis only.
Power Factor Charge, per kVAr $ 1.10
name: Schedule BP Bulk Power Industrial, Demand Metered 7,000 kW and Over, Time-Of-Use
